{"tid":167843,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"夕陽之歌真係好好聽","createTime":"2017-03-23T06:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T10:29:27.000Z","uid":3599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8497dd181338190959b7fc87a9f795c5914c1fa","tid":167843,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"聽第一句啲眼淚已經不停流<br />\n<br />\n斜陽無限 無奈只一息間燦爛<br />\n隨雲霞漸散 逝去的光彩不復還<br />\n遲遲年月 難耐這一生的變幻<br />\n如浮雲聚散 纏結這滄桑的倦顏<br />\n漫長路驟覺光陰退減 歡欣總短暫未再返<br />\n那個看透我夢想是平淡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34758287dfa07fe11109652a5c28b850e9532cf9","tid":167843,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:47:23.000Z","msg":"無人覺得好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01f12d3a88510dad1cf07c85177f3955d1d530b","tid":167843,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從前你呀媽 煲𡃁湯</span></span>"},{"pid":"16b8907cf709447b8b0d0de8c47f88fef60c6646","tid":167843,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從前你呀媽 煲𡃁湯</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad98e17146ac430b57cc4fb520803957b8a57787","tid":167843,"uid":92628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"歌者更提升左首歌既層次"},{"pid":"d7024cf9912d038bf60c9af5fa81dfa6e4b3e4a6","tid":167843,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"有次唱k有個fd唱呢曲，我我夾硬唱千千闕歌搞到佢要跟我一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d231686e77c367d8e5cd5b2eb836cecc82d3c357","tid":167843,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歌者更提升左首歌既層次</blockquote><br />\n佢個告別演唱會既版本令首歌更加淒楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d21e76418e301ab87e0257912ea014be060ee6","tid":167843,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次唱k有個fd唱呢曲，我我夾硬唱千千闕歌搞到佢要跟我一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常身邊啲人都唔會聽舊歌"},{"pid":"b3ebfca9cbb2a7ed0c4480d6423e935d44ebd248","tid":167843,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:29:27.000Z","msg":"首歌真係好好聽好有味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家啲歌冇深度剩係識洗腦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過套戲好悶"}]}